      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TOFFEE WAR (2) has been a little hard to follow, finishing out of the placings latest but was in winning form two back scoring in a Maiden at this track. Expecting significant improvement this line-up. HOT HONEY (8) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (25.10) in a T3 RSTW at Sale. Has never missed the frame here at the trip from four starts. The form from her last run stacks up well. Should be thereabouts. VICE LIKE GRIP (7) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (23.17) at this track behind Brindle Mosaic in a Rank Limit - Restricted Win. Has the pace to be prominent. Can feature again. MERRY MYRTLE (4) cannot be left out after placing at a big quote last start.",
